{"tid":790650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真 有冇人覺得環保撚同女權撚好多都鳩鳩地","createTime":"2018-08-23T07:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T09:32:57.000Z","uid":14719,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b450da8450632a3d87f750e37371062b09daeb","tid":790650,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"環保撚成日話走膠走飲管 諸多限制 但又好少見佢地講有咩有效替代方法<br />\n又唔諗下唔用呢啲嘢會有幾唔方便<br />\n用飲管驚唔衛生 用膠袋為咗易拎嘢 <br />\n但啲環保撚好多都淨係識得ban人 有啲仲惡到見人用膠就掟上網批鬥<br />\n問佢有咩替代方法 一係就唔可行/成效低 一係就適得其反 <br />\n好似starfuck個新杯 話就話冇飲管 但啲膠仲多咗<br />\n又好似話為咗減少膠袋 就整多咗環保袋攞去派＋支持膠袋收費 去鼓勵啲人用環保袋 結果製造更多污染<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不織布袋倍增 膠袋稅加劇污染：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20110718/00407_020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110718%2F00407_020.html&d=rHqTbPGR3zbQL8maV%2FRfIG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=45e5477f\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20110718/00407_020.html</a><br />\n<br />\n女權撚 成日話乜女性地位<br />\n好似講到只要一份工/部分職位男多過女 就係特登歧視女性 打壓女性上位咁<br />\n又話啲人淨係留意男子世界盃 女子世界盃無人留意係因為男性主義嘅錯 <br />\n又唔見啲人講咩女排 女網不平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/212703_4b1d022667ca9907fff4c44d37428521.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F212703_4b1d022667ca9907fff4c44d37428521.jpeg&h=269a85a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲又話乜鳩物化女性<br />\n講佢兩句壞話 話佢肥 話佢矮就物化 但讚佢靚佢又受喎<br />\n但班友批評男人 話人樣衰 話人毒撚樣 又ok喎<br />\n簡單啲講咪即係有着數個陣就當冇嘢 一有少少蝕底就高呼反父權社會 要求女性平等"},{"pid":"c0c151758d4a4bbe1daeb197f878fe2e0d74691f","tid":790650,"uid":34553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"好耐之前戲院都係免費用3D眼鏡<br />\n睇完戲就俾返戲院<br />\n之後話環保原因變咗要人買副<br />\n大佬好多時都係興起去睇戲<br />\n邊會帶副嘢出街<br />\n依家屋企起碼有廿副<br />\n<br />\n香港講環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b7f995d60667fa27ddd3a4b84027af4d0c938c","tid":790650,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"左膠一向"},{"pid":"253df16be88b8607bc96b510fa7e065b97b8b30c","tid":790650,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩上fb睇完依d女權撚d post<br />\n真係仇男毒西黎 係唔係冇男人要佢所以佢先咁憎男人"},{"pid":"211713e963b495d7e70d0255212213c96e725fe6","tid":790650,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"仲有素食撚,羊肉當狗肉批鬥人,唔畀素食餐廳員工放飯時食肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500f0da4bf547d29d505cd7e8fcc0ae628e6ff31","tid":790650,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"好多素食撚都係女人黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f710c3cdc6d5c614b3638b8147a150822a656d","tid":790650,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都霸道到仆街"},{"pid":"0199f2b5f8ac1c34f3dda233c825dfa3288f9cc5","tid":790650,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0c151758d4a4bbe1daeb197f878fe2e0d74691f","tid":790650,"uid":34553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"好耐之前戲院都係免費用3D眼鏡<br />\n睇完戲就俾返戲院<br />\n之後話環保原因變咗要人買副<br />\n大佬好多時都係興起去睇戲<br />\n邊會帶副嘢出街<br />\n依家屋企起碼有廿副<br />\n<br />\n香港講環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:10:40.000Z","msg":"中資 ua <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f2a8223b5e63632507ebe14f99504b48d57a1c","tid":790650,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500f0da4bf547d29d505cd7e8fcc0ae628e6ff31","tid":790650,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-2